    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute gem! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a dent in sight, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It drives like a dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
