    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and scent-fresh, with zero signs of bolster wear or aging. Every electronic component and convenience feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records meticulously organized and available. Driven sparingly and always garage-kept under a breathable cover, this is a collector-grade find for the most discerning enthusiast. No accidents, no smoke, and no stories\u2014just absolute perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
