    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it\u2019s like it just left the dealership! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it's sparkling clean inside and out without a single blemish to be found. It runs perfectly and feels just like new. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one! Can't wait for you to take it for a spin!",
