      "description": "An exceptional S54-powered E46 M3 that defies its vintage. This specimen features a meticulously maintained 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a recently overhauled double-VANOS system. The chassis is structurally pristine, with a reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec suspension geometry. Gear shifts are tactile and precise through the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, feeding a healthy limited-slip differential. The paint remains in concours state with consistent micron readings, while the interior leather shows no bolster wear. A mechanically synchronized, investment-grade driver\u2019s car.",
